com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.log

Interface ChangeProcessor


  • public interface ChangeProcessor
    Allows the user to define custom behavior to process those transactional changes that are recorded in a transaction log. ChangeProcessors are registered with a transaction log processor in the LogProcessorBuilder.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
